    },
    {
      "start": 199.02,
      "end": 201.46,
      "text": "He actually was on a phone call with Zoe."
    },
    {
      "start": 201.64,
      "end": 202.0,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 202.16,
      "end": 203.54,
      "text": "They were talking about the scene."
    },
    {
      "start": 203.54,
      "end": 203.82,
      "text": "The audition."
    },
    {
      "start": 204.1,
      "end": 204.52,
      "text": "Audition."
    },
    {
      "start": 204.72,
      "end": 207.12,
      "text": "And it was the actual Jason Mraz."
    },
    {
      "start": 207.52,
      "end": 207.86,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 207.86,
      "end": 216.26,
      "text": "그리고 거의 영화의 막바지에 한 번 더 출연을 하는데, 그때 완전 딱 봐도 그냥 Jason Mraz이었어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 216.3,
      "end": 217.04,
      "text": "이제 울고까지."
    },
    {
      "start": 217.16,
      "end": 217.54,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 217.54,
      "end": 220.16,
      "text": "So first it was his voice, now it's his face."
    },
    {
      "start": 220.4,
      "end": 225.46,
      "text": "The character and the real Jason Mraz looked too much alike, 그쵸?"
