    {
      "start": 238.5,
      "end": 238.76,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 239.8,
      "end": 241.58,
      "text": "Anyway, it was the real Jason Mraz."
    },
    {
      "start": 241.74,
      "end": 245.76,
      "text": "Yeah, 근데 이 Jason Mraz가 was interested in acting, wasn't he?"
    },
    {
      "start": 245.94,
      "end": 246.68,
      "text": "Actually, yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 246.68,
      "end": 251.02,
      "text": "To begin with, back in high school, he started with acting."
    },
    {
      "start": 251.18,
      "end": 256.96,
      "text": "He performed in high school musicals and plays, and he really loved acting."
    },
    {
      "start": 257.78,
      "end": 263.96,
      "text": "And then he went actually to the American Musical and Dramatic Academy in New York City,"
    },
    {
      "start": 263.96,
      "end": 266.24,
      "text": "which is a professional acting school."
    },
    {
      "start": 266.46,
      "end": 273.52,
      "text": "He was there for about a year and a half, and his original plan was to work, to make money in musical theater."
    },
    {
      "start": 274.06,
      "end": 280.36,
      "text": "And then things changed when a friend gave him a guitar that he was going to throw away."
    },
    {
      "start": 280.36,
      "end": 280.76,
      "text": "Wow."
    },
    {
      "start": 280.82,
      "end": 282.84,
      "text": "He said, here, you can have it."
    },
    {
      "start": 282.94,
      "end": 283.3,
      "text": "Wow."
    },
    {
      "start": 283.38,
      "end": 284.34,
      "text": "I don't want to throw it away."
    },
    {
      "start": 284.4,
      "end": 285.0,
      "text": "You use it."
    },
    {
      "start": 285.1,
      "end": 285.46,
      "text": "Wow."
    },
    {
      "start": 285.64,
      "end": 286.48,
      "text": "He learned to play guitar."
    },
    {
      "start": 286.88,
      "end": 288.42,
      "text": "He ended up in San Diego."
    },
    {
      "start": 288.6,
      "end": 288.86,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 289.02,
      "end": 293.84,
      "text": "And my friend, way back then, used to see him perform in San Diego."
    },
    {
      "start": 293.84,
      "end": 301.1,
      "text": "Before he was big and famous, he performed every week at a local coffee house with just him and a drum."
    },
    {
      "start": 301.3,
      "end": 303.34,
      "text": "And sometimes a bass player joined him."
    },
    {
      "start": 303.54,
      "end": 309.1,
      "text": "And my friend was always talking about this singer and said, oh, he was so good."
    },
    {
      "start": 309.18,
      "end": 311.48,
      "text": "And when he became famous, he said, I knew it."
    },
    {
      "start": 311.48,
      "end": 312.74,
      "text": "I knew it."
    },
    {
      "start": 312.82,
      "end": 313.78,
      "text": "I saw it coming."
    },
    {
      "start": 314.1,
      "end": 320.72,
      "text": "내가 그 제이슨 라즈를 뜨기 전부터 잘될 줄 알았단 말이지 라는 이야기를 계속 하시는 거죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 320.94,
      "end": 322.3,
      "text": "내가 안목이 뛰어나지."
    },
    {
      "start": 322.94,
